------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Third-party components
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Reame is built on llama.cpp (https://github.com/ggml-org/llama.cpp), included
as a git submodule under third_party/llama.cpp and licensed under the MIT
License. All tensor kernels and GGUF handling come from llama.cpp; Reame adds
the memory layer, serving, and orchestration on top. llama.cpp is not modified
in place and keeps its own license.
